		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="441" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雳震化身飞快使用自身翼片旋转，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">20%x3</span><span>伤害，并在攻击范围边缘产生8道落雷，均造成</span><span color="#ffacff">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="414" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雳震化身甩下3道线性落雷，呈扇形分布，落雷造成<span color="#ffacff">30%,15%,7.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雳震化身在身边唤出5枚闪雷球，并慢慢旋转，触碰持续造成<span color="#ffacff">10%,5%,2.5%,1%</span><span>伤害，最终闪雷球被引爆，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="437" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雳震化身即刻展开<span textDecoration="underline">试炼领域</span><span>，并获得</span><span textDecoration="underline">白护盾</span><span>，从领域内不断产生向外的互相垂直的4道万钧之箔，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，重复3回，最后收回领域并产生鸣震之斥，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，所剩的护盾将转为等量</span><span textDecoration="underline">沃陆之灵御</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
